{"tid":2204190,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過抆抆下屎張廁紙斷咗","createTime":"2020-09-16T01:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T14:06:47.000Z","uid":4895,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"052b6545c433558b7b5099608b0f133f91cc3793","tid":2204190,"uid":4895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:12:24.000Z","msg":"唔知大家抆屎時有冇習慣會用張廁紙包住隻手指然後塞小小入去屎眼到了2下確保冇哂屎漬<br />\n<br />\n點知啱啱發覺了極都仲有漬<br />\n就再塞多小小入去了啦<br />\n當我塞哂成隻手指入去果陣<br />\n張廁紙就zip住咗係個屎眼到<br />\n又抆唔返出黎<br />\n<br />\n我已經即刻用水沖佢希望可以痾返佢出黎<br />\n再好似冇乜效果<br />\n<br />\n呢家感覺到個屎眼透唔到氣好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2311436971b832f38905fe6e97a2e739e0e17c","tid":2204190,"uid":199297,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:17:25.000Z","msg":"咁唯有下次屙屎用啲屎推返張紙巾出黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c514413a67cbcd2d8a6c1f72731da8f7dffa7e63","tid":2204190,"uid":4895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca2311436971b832f38905fe6e97a2e739e0e17c","tid":2204190,"uid":199297,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:17:25.000Z","msg":"咁唯有下次屙屎用啲屎推返張紙巾出黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:21:28.000Z","msg":"呢家坐係到都覺得有野頂住"},{"pid":"b826d23f332425524058a20966c79ec9112ede3c","tid":2204190,"uid":1734,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:29:54.000Z","msg":"你主人幫你抆？"},{"pid":"5f389cd2883aa75c3e3e0323d88803ea5690c662","tid":2204190,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T01:33:47.000Z","msg":"拎kfc手套撩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840277c6fa3dd42705112ee49ef0aaa7d06a07db","tid":2204190,"uid":11365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f389cd